.SH NAME
hvc_iucv_notifier_add \- HVC notifier for opening a TTY for the first time.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" hvc_iucv_notifier_add
.BI "(struct hvc_struct *hp "  ","
.BI "int id "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hp" 12
Pointer to the HVC device (struct hvc_struct)
.IP "id" 12
Additional data (originally passed to hvc_alloc): the index of an struct
hvc_iucv_private instance.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
The function sets the tty state to TTY_OPENED for the struct hvc_iucv_private
instance that is derived from \fIid\fP. Always returns 0.

Locking:     struct hvc_iucv_private->lock, spin_lock_bh
